2003-08-27 13:13  gordon

	* filters/comeagain.py: Added new module that forces any previously
	unknown sender to send their message a second time.  Most spamware
	and virusware won't do this, so the filter should cut down on the
	amount of unwanted traffic into the domain.  Some mailing lists
	won't put up with this behavior, though.

